derivation: from G1 (ἀδύνατος) (as a negative particle) and G1415 (ἀδύνατος);
kjv_def: could not do, impossible, impotent, not possible, weak
strongs_def: unable, i.e. weak (literally or figuratively); passively, impossible
outline:
1. without strength, impotent, powerless, weakly, disabled
  2. unable to be done, impossible
